          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Nothing Off Balance Sheet Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Securities and Exchange Commission, in establishing accounting principles or standards under the securities laws, to require any person subject to those principles or standards to show all transactions on the person's balance sheet.</p>]]></text>
